{"tid":1901631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港1月樓價指數按月跌近0.2%連跌兩個月 私樓租金指數連跌五個月！","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T02:27:42.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f92cc552a2fa131ab5742317563cc7f66765c3a","tid":1901631,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb868f39f4f9c465f55cd1aa5ea102ae2831608","tid":1901631,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"本港樓價連跌兩個月，上月跌幅較前月收窄。<br />\n<br />\n差餉物業估價署公布，1月私人住宅售價指數跌至378.2，按月跌近0.2%，跌幅較去年12月的近1.6%收窄；數據按年升近4.8%。<br />\n<br />\n上月私樓租金指數連跌5個月，按月跌2.1%至185.6，跌幅創5個月以來最大；數據按年跌近3.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511382-20200228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511382-20200228.htm&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0eIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=274ad152\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511382-20200228.htm&h=7fad4505\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511382-20200228.htm</a>"},{"pid":"494b20277ba19c7e8f86168c3b517fbd798750a1","tid":1901631,"uid":288913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"車厘龜？"},{"pid":"49610c3d93f80c088157c76b6bb75c76f680be3a","tid":1901631,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"車厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3728b985becd2b14f0e2c101854ca14f0a3e8373","tid":1901631,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kX83PiS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkX83PiS.gif&h=9dd04d3d&s={